Package: AIafter
Title: Forecast Combination Using the AI-AFTER Algorithm
Version: 1.1
Author: Wei Qian, Craig A. Rolling, Gang Cheng, Yuhong Yang
Maintainer: Wei Qian <weiqian@udel.edu>
Description: This package implements the AI-AFTER algorithm for forecast combination. AI-AFTER first determines the appropriate combining goal (adaptation vs. improvement) and then combines the forecasts to achieve optimal performance of the proper goal.
License: GPL-2
Depends: forecast,ncvreg,MASS,quadprog
